Generic single-database configuration for DigniLife.

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for managing database schema changes.

## Usage

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migration
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
alembic history
```

### View current version
```bash
alembic current
```

## Important Notes

- Always review autogenerated migrations before applying them
- Test migrations on development/staging before production
- Never edit migrations after they've been applied to production
- Always backup database before running migrations on production
